an Beach brought capes, centipedes and pure San Francisco vibes to the city’s streets. ","abstract":"\u003cp\u003eThe 12-kilometer race from the Embarcadero to Ocean Beach brought capes, centipedes and pure San Francisco vibes to the city’s streets. \u003c/p\u003e","plainTextAbstract":"The 12-kilometer race from the Embarcadero to Ocean Beach brought capes, centipedes and pure San Francisco vibes to the city’s streets. ","displayedDate":"2026-05-17 12:26:05","lastModifiedDate":"2026-05-17 17:06:52","elapsedTime":null,"authorName":null,"authorHref":null,"authors":[{"id":7147,"name":"Lucy Hodgman","title":"Staff writer","url":"/author/lucy-hodgman/","credit":null,"image":{"id":null,"url":"https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/41/45/13/25580281/4/rawImage.jpg","base64":null,"width":1111,"height":700,"guid":null,"dirPath":null,"alt":"Lucy Hodgman is a Hearst Fellow covering politics and policy with the Capitol Bureau.","title":"Lucy Hodgman"}}],"bylineObjects":[{"id":7147,"name":"Lucy Hodgman","title":"Staff writer","url":"/author/lucy-hodgman/","credit":"Staff Writer","image":{"id":25580281,"url":null,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":1111,"height":700,"guid":"photo_25580281","dirPath":"01/41/45/13/25580281/4","alt":"Lucy Hodgman is a Hearst Fellow covering politics and policy with the Capitol Bureau.","title":"Lucy Hodgman"}}],"eyebrow":{"isPublished":true,"linkText":"San Francisco","url":"/sf/"},"badge":null,"image":{"url":"https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/66/23/20/31011863/3/rawImage.jpg","b64":null,"width":2048,"height":1366,"caption":{"plain":"Particpants run through Golden Gate Park during the 114th annual Bay to Breakers race in San Francisco, May 17, 2026.","html1":null,"serializedReact":null},"loading":"lazy","external":null,"alt":"Participants in the 113th annual Bay to Breakers run through Golden Gate Park at the end of the 12-kilometer race. ","title":"breakers0517_WEB_162689535"},"collectionConfig":{"showLabels":false,"persistentTimestamp":false,"showEyebrow